      Key Features
    </h2>
    <ul
      class="list-disc pl-5 text-gray-700 dark:text-dark-text-secondary transition-colors duration-300"
    >
      <li>Role assignment and management</li>
      <li>Search functionality for users</li>
      <li>View and handle role requests</li>
      <li>Secure and easy-to-use interface</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div
    class="mt-8 bg-white dark:bg-dark-surface shadow-lg rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-dark-border transition-colors duration-300"
  >
    <h2
      class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-dark-text-primary mb-4 transition-colors duration-300"
    >
      Technologies Used
    </h2>
    <ul
      class="list-disc pl-5 text-gray-700 dark:text-dark-text-secondary transition-colors duration-300"
    >
      <li>Node.js and Express.js for backend</li>
      <li>EJS for templating</li>
      <li>Tailwind CSS for styling</li>
      <li>MongoDB for database management</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

