    >
      Core Team Members
    </h2>
    <ul
      class="list-disc pl-5 text-gray-700 dark:text-dark-text-secondary transition-colors duration-300"
    >
      <li><strong>Sanskar Gupta</strong> - Developer & Project Lead</li>
      <li><strong>Shivam Jha</strong> - Developer & Backend Specialist</li>
